            "text": "1 Chronicles 29:25",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The Lord magnified Solomon exceedingly — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Gave him great honour and reputation, together with riches and power, and all such things as render a king great and glorious. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Bestowed upon him such royal majesty as had not been on any king of Israel — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Either on David or Saul, or any of the former governors of Israel. None of his predecessors possessed such dignity and authority, or lived in such splendour and magnificence as he did.",
        "children": []
